summary: Adds 6 different sets of light armor female only.
descriptionHtml:
Dark Wind armor for UNP
Author: Fizz
Version:3.0
Date: 03/23/2012

======================
Description
======================

Adds 6 different sets of light armor female only.

Additem 
xx001da3  Dark wind v3
xx000d65  Dark wind v2
xx000d62  Dark wind v1

xx00230f  Dark wind shirt v1
xx002311  Dark wind shirt v2
xx002313  Dark wind shirt v3

xx001dab  Dark wind gloves
xx001da9  Dark wind boots


xx = Darkwindv1.esp load order.
======================
Requirements:
======================

DIMONIZED UNP female body
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=6709

======================
Uninstall
======================

Delete those folders

Skyrim\\Data\\meshes\\fizz\\darkwind

Skyrim\\Data\\textures\\fizz\\darkwind

And
Darkwindv1.esp
Skyrim\\Data\\
